:: Gwylan Gifts List
<<effects>>

What gift would you like to give Gwylan?
<br><br>

<<food_gift_list>>

<<if _food_gift_found is true>>
	<<skinicon "give">><<link [[Give gift (0:05)|Gwylan Gifts]]>><<pass 5>><<give_gift Gwylan>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<refuseicon>><<link [[Reconsider|Gwylan Gifts List Reconsider]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Gifts List Reconsider
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

<<if $location is "forest_shop">>
	Gwylan continues rummaging around for something, not noticing your reconsideration at all.
<<else>>
	Gwylan continues staring out at the sea, not noticing your reconsideration at all.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Gifts
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set _gift to $gift.name + ($gift.handheld_gift ? " gift" : "")>>
<<wearProp _gift>>

<<if $phase is 1>>
	"I've brought you something," you say.
<<elseif $phase is 2>>
	"I made something," you say. "Just for you."
<<else>>
	"I've made you a gift," you say. "I hope you like it."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if $gift.name is "plum_pudding">>
	You hold out the plum pudding.
	<<if _gwylanTF.known and $location is "forest_shop">>
		Gwylan's eyes light up, and <<his>> fox ears stand up straight.
	<<else>>
		Gwylan's eyes light up.
	<</if>>
	"Oh my. You certainly know the fastest way to a <<personsimple>>'s heart." <<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><<gyearning>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> takes a large bite of it. "Made with real plums, too! Perfection." <<He>> closes <<his>> eyes and places a hand on <<his>> cheek as <<he>> chews. "I adore plums. The perfect texture and balance of sweetness and tartness. You could even taste it without a tongue."
	<br><br>
	<<saveFavoriteFood "Gwylan" $gift.name>>
	<<earnFeat "Coven Comforts">>

	<<He>> opens <<his>> eyes and blushes, realising <<hes>> already eaten half of it. "Oh dear, how rude of me. This would taste much better shared."
	<<if $location is "forest_shop">>
		<<He>> nods to a small table tucked away in the corner of the shop.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Let Gwylan have all of it|Gwylan Gifts Plum]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Share it|Gwylan Gifts Plum Share]]>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 1>><</link>><<glust>>
	<br>
<<elseif $gift.name is "valentines_chocolate" and $valentines>>
	<<earnFeat "Be My Valentine">>
	You hold out the heart-shaped box of valentines chocolates. Gwylan leans forward and sniffs it.
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
		"Chocolates?" <<he>> asks. "For Valentine's Day! Why, I will be your Valentine, dear!" <<He>> flips open the box, and bites one of the chocolates in half.<<ggyearning>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 3>>
		<br><br>
		
		<<He>> licks <<his>> upper lip. "It tastes excellent. But then, anything made by you tastes good." <<He>> catches <<himself>> before biting another. "I hope I'm not breaking a convention by scoffing them straight away." <<He>> thinks a moment, then shrugs, and devours another. "As if I could resist your chocolate."
		<br><br>
		<<He>> scoffs yet another, then puts the box away for later.
		<br><br>
	<<else>>
		"Chocolates?" <<he>> asks. "For little old me?"<<ggyearning>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 3>>
		<br><br>

		<<He>> opens the box, and appears to enjoy savouring the sight of them. "Are there any conventions? Can I eat them now?" Without waiting for an answer, <<he>> takes a chocolate, and bites it in half. "I'd say your talents are wasted on me, but that's for you to decide."
		<br><br>
		<<He>> scoffs another, then puts the box away for later.
		<br><br>
	<</if>>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<<elseif $gift.special.includes("spicy")>>
	You hold out the <<recipe_name $gift.name>>. Gwylan tilts <<his>> head.
	<<if $location is "cafe" and !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
		"How did you sneak that past Sammy? Never mind, I'm sure I can squeeze that in alongside breakfast."
	<</if>>

	<<He>> smells it. "A spicy dish? I have trouble tasting those. I'm willing to try, though."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> takes a bite, and chews. <<His>> expression remains neutral. "Sorry, dear. I'm afraid I can't taste it at all." <<He>> smiles. "I won't let it go to waste, though. It might taste better shared."
	<<if $location is "forest_shop">>
		<<He>> nods to a small table tucked away in the corner of the shop.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Let Gwylan have all of it|Gwylan Gifts Spicy]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Share it|Gwylan Gifts Spicy Share]]>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 1>><</link>><<glust>>
	<br>

<<elseif $gift.special.includes("drink")>>
	You hold out the <<recipe_name $gift.name>>. <<He>> tilts <<his>> head. "A brew of your own? I'm intrigued." <<He>> gently takes it in both hands and smells it. "Interesting." <<He>> swirls it, before taking a small sip. The small sip quickly turns into <<him>> chugging it.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Gifts Drink End]]>><</link>>
<<else>>
	You hold out the <<recipe_name $gift.name>>.
	<<if $location is "cafe" and !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
		"How did you sneak that past Sammy? Never mind, I'm sure I can squeeze that in alongside breakfast."
	<</if>>

	<<He>> inspects it for a moment, before taking it in <<his>> hands. "It smells wonderful," <<he>> says. "I'm sure it tastes just as good. It would taste better shared, though."
	<<if $location is "forest_shop">>
		<<He>> nods to a small table tucked away in the corner of the shop.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Let Gwylan have all of it|Gwylan Gifts Food]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Share it|Gwylan Gifts Food Share]]>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 1>><</link>><<glust>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Gifts Plum
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
You shake your head, and insist on <<him>> eating it all.
<br><br>

<<if $location is "forest_shop">>
	The whole shop seems to brighten up for a little while after <<he>> finishes it.
<<else>>
	<<He>> continues watching the sea as <<he>> finishes it. <<Hes>> practically glowing.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte 50>>
	"You deserve a treat too, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>."
	<<if $location is "cafe" and !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
		<<He>> leans over the table and gives you a quick peck on the cheek.
	<<else>>
		<<He>> leans over the counter and gives you a quick peck on the cheek.
	<</if>>
	<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
		"Don't think about that too much," <<he>> says with a blush.
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	"That was very thoughtful of you, dear. Thank you."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Gifts Plum Share
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $location is "forest_shop">>
	<<He>> leads you over to the small table, before disappearing through a dark doorway.
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("dog_bowl")>>
		<<if _gwylanStatus.includesAny("dom", "lust") or $gwylanSeen.includes("dog_bowl_name")>>
			<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("dog_bowl_name")>>
				<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("dog_bowl_name")>>
				<<He>> returns with a <span class="pink">clean dog bowl</span>, which <<he>> puts in front of you.
				It's different from last time. Small gems are embedded around it, and <span class="pink">your name is engraved on the side</span>.
				<br><br>

				Gwylan sways back and forth, blushing. "You've been such a <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "good">> for me, so I thought I'd make something to show you just how much I appreciate you, too. I hope you like it." <<npcincr Gwylan dom 5>><<ggyearning>>
				<br><br>
			<<else>>
				<<He>> returns with <span class="pink">your dog bowl</span>.
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<He>> returns with a <span class="pink">clean dog bowl</span>, which <<he>> puts in front of you.
		<</if>>
		<<He>> places the remaining pudding in it.
	<<else>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("dog_bowl")>>
		"Oh no. I'm all out of clean dishes. Unless..." You hear some dishes clanking around.
		<br><br>

		<<He>> re-emerges, and places a <span class="pink">clean dog bowl</span> in front of you. <<He>> blushes as <<he>> puts the rest of the pudding in it. "I'm sorry about this, dear. I promise it's sanitary."
		<<if $worn.neck.collared is 1>>
			<<He>> looks at your collar. "I have a feeling you don't mind."
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Eat normally|Gwylan Gifts Food Pet Normal]]>><<set $phase to "plum">><<stress -2>><</link>><<lstress>>
	<br>
	<<if hasSexStat("deviancy", 2)>>
		<<link [[Eat like a pet|Gwylan Gifts Food Petplay]]>><<set $phase to "plum">><<npcincr Gwylan lust 4>><</link>><<deviant2>><<gglust>>
	<<else>>
		<<insufficientStat "deviancy" "to eat like a pet">>
	<</if>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<He>> places half of what remains of the pudding on your plate. You did a good job. It's quite tasty.
	<br><br>

	<<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte 50>>
		"You deserve a treat too, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>."
		<<if $location is "cafe" and !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
			<<He>> leans over the table and gives you a quick peck on the cheek.
		<<else>>
			<<He>> leans over the counter and gives you a quick peck on the cheek.
		<</if>>
		<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
			"Don't think about that too much," <<he>> says with a blush.
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		"That was very thoughtful of you, dear. Thank you."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Gifts Spicy
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
Gwylan eats in silence. It really doesn't seem like <<hes>> able to taste it at all. "I'm sure it's delicious," <<he>> says. "I appreciate the thought."
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Gifts Spicy Share
