	<br><br>

	"Thank you for the meal, dear."
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanOptions>>
<</if>>


:: Gwylan Gifts Food Pet Normal
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
You eat from the bowl with utensils, like a normal person.
<br><br>

<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance") or _gwylanStatus.includes("lust")>>
	Gwylan stares at you, elbows on the table and head in <<his>> hands, as if you were the most interesting thing in the world.
	<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
		<<His>> tail flits back and forth behind <<him>>.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	When you've finished, <<he>> walks around the table and pets your head.
	<<if $phase is "plum">>
		"You're so thoughtful, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>."
		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners") or _gwylanStatus.includes("lust")>>
			<<He>> wraps <<his>> arms around you and kisses you on the cheek.
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "good">>."
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	Gwylan keeps looking up at you.
	<<if $phase is "plum">>
		"This was very thoughtful of you, dear. Thank you."
	<<elseif $phase is "spicy">>
		"Even if I can't taste it, I can enjoy eating it with you," <<he>> says. "It adds just the slightest hint of sweetness."
	<<else>>
		"Thank you for the meal, dear."
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

Gwylan takes care of the dishes, before returning to the counter.
<br><br>

<<set $phase to 0>>
<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Gifts Food Petplay
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("petplay")>>
You lean your head down, eating and licking your food
<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 3>>
	like a good little pet. <<hypnosisText "You're such a good pet for <<gwylanHypnoName>>. The thought fills you with joy and bliss. <<trauma -2>><<ltrauma>>">>
<<else>>
	as if you were Gwylan's pet.
<</if>>
<<deviancy2>>

<<He>> giggles, and walks around the table. <<He>> pets the back of your head, and you lean into it.
<<if $phase is "plum">>
	"You're so thoughtful, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>."
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners") or _gwylanStatus.includes("lust")>>
		<<He>> wraps <<his>> arms around you and kisses you on the cheek.
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "good">>."
<</if>>
<br><br>

You lick your bowl clean. Gwylan takes care of the dishes, before returning to the counter.
<br><br>

<<set $phase to 0>>
<<gwylanOptions>>


:: Gwylan Gifts Drink End
<<effects>>

<<He>> lets out a refreshed sigh. "That was delicious. Thank you, dear. May I keep the container? I could fill it with small seashells, or some such." You nod, which prompts <<him>> to smile.
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>
